(3372, 3, '2016-06-20 15:28:37', '2016-06-20 15:28:37', '[tg_header title="An Intimate Journey into the Heart of Rural Nepal" subtitle="A Socially Conscious Adventure"]\r\nMake a lasting difference while living the adventure of a lifetime. More than just a trek, Nepalaya Explorer''s Community Trek Nepal is a total immersion experience for those searching for more fulfillment from their travel abroad. You will become part of a close-knit team striving to bring medical, social, educational, and economic aid to villages destroyed by the 2015 earthquakes. From your vantage point within these small communities, you will learn about the traitional Nepali way of life while exploring areas largely unfamiliar to international guests.\r\n\r\nPhysical activities are of moderate difficulty and no prior experience is necessary.\r\n<br>\r\n[tg_header title="Quick Look" subtitle="Adventure Overview"]\r\n<strong>Who should go: </strong>Students, outdoor enthusiasts, teachers, anyone wishing to share his or her knowledge on subjects of civic importance, or who would like to have an intimate view of the traditional rural Nepali lifestyle\r\n<strong>Trip Duration: </strong>15 - 30 days\r\n<b>Physical Difficulty: </b>2 of 5\r\n<strong>Activities: </strong>Community service work, community education, cultural immersion, cooking, trekking\r\n<strong>Max. Altitude: </strong>\r\n<strong>Group Size: </strong>2-14\r\n<strong>Accommodations: </strong>Homestay, guesthouse\r\n\r\n[tg_header title="You will enjoy:"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Assisting with medical checkups, distribution of medicine, and referrals for follow-up care</li>\r\n	<li>Constructing a safe and educational children''s playground, including a multi-sport arena</li>\r\n	<li>Organizing community workshops on a variety of topics, including: caring for the environment, politics, ecotourism, traffic safety, sex education, water safety and irrigation, civic engagement, and workplace training</li>\r\n	<li>Helping Nepali teens build outdoor adventure skills in activities such as: rafting, trekking, mountain biking, rock climbing, canyoning, and swimming</li>\r\n	<li>Learning about and preserving Nepali culture and traditions</li>\r\n	<li>Discovering Nepali cuisine, recipes, and culinary techniques</li>\r\n	<li>Educating the community about rubbish collection, recycling, and reducing waste by re-using resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[tg_header title="Adventure Program" subtitle="15 to 30 Days"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEach Community Trek Nepal is a unique adventure. Where you will go, and exactly which activities you will participate in are dependent on village partners and ongoing recovery efforts. If you would like a detailed itinerary for the dates you will be traveling to Nepal, please contact us for more information.\r\n\r\n[tg_header title="Price Includes:"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Domestic transportation</li>\r\n	<li>Accommodation</li>\r\n	<li>3 meals daily</li>\r\n	<li>All associated permits</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[tg_header title="Price Does Not Include:"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>International flights and associated taxes</li>\r\n	<li>Nepali tourist visa</li>\r\n	<li>Optional (*) activities</li>\r\n	<li>Alcoholic and specialty beverages</li>\r\n	<li>Tips for porters and guides</li>\r\n	<li>Travel and health insurance</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Community Trek Nepal', '<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>&nbsp;4-5 Stars Hotel for all trips\r\n<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>&nbsp;Chill out on historical town and city of madrid\r\n<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>&nbsp;Watch La li ga football match\r\n<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>&nbsp;100% Satisfaction guarantee', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2807-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-20 15:28:37', '2016-06-20 15:28:37', '', 2807, 'http://nepalayaexplorer.com/2016/06/20/2807-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
